snippet: Victoria Azarenka, a two-time champion and a former No. 1, missed out on a seeding at the Australian Open after falling in the rankings to No. 41.
abstract: Former tennis champion Victoria Azarenka misses seeding at the Australian Open after falling in overall women's rankings to No 41 in first weeks of 2015.
lead_paragraph: Victoria Azarenka, a two-time champion and a former No. 1, missed out on a seeding at the Australian Open after falling in the rankings to No. 41.

headline.main: Azarenka Isn’t Seeded for Australian Open
